
   #  Types
   
      +  Metadata Checkpointing
         -  Used to recover from Driver failure in node running Driver application
         -  Some Metadata,
            .  Configuration
            .  DStream operation etc...
            
      +  Data Checkpointing
         -  Is saving of generated RDDs to reliable storage
         
   #  When to enable Checkpointing?
      +  When stateful transformation is used
      +  When need to recover from Driver failure
      
   #  How to configure?
      +  Done using
         -  streamingContext.checkpoint(checkPointDirectory)
      +  Check example & more information here...
         -  http://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/streaming-programming-guide.html#how-to-configure-checkpointing
                                 